# Pricing (two systems)

## Bachelor / Master

- **UI:** `.kalkulator-wse` in `template-parts/prices/calculator.php`.
- **Wiring:** `section_tuition_fees.php` → `bachelor-master/section-tuition-calculator.php` (needs post meta `logical_sync_key`).
- **Data:** `akademiataPrices.googleApiUrl` (Apps Script); JS `assets/src/js/prices-calculator.js` (bundled in `main.js`); optional fallback `prices.json`.
- **Header teaser:** link “SPRAWDZ CENNIK” to `#tuition_fees` when `logical_sync_key` is set (no CPT price row).

## Postgraduate / MBA

- **Data:** ACF on the offer post — `payments`, `full_time`, `part_time`, column title fields, `more_info`.
- **PHP:** `configure/offer-pricing.php` (`akademiata_pg_mba_*`).
- **Templates:** `template-parts/single-offer/pg-mba/` (`section-tuition-fees.php`, `partials/price-table-acf.php`, `tuition-payments.php`, `bank-transfer-info.php`).
- **Payments repeater:** title, price, currency, optional `description` (no `promotion` checkbox on rows).
- **Table promos:** column flags like `add_promotion_rat8` in `full_time` / `part_time` grids.
- **Teaser price:** `akademiata_pg_mba_get_teaser_price_text()` from first row `col_8_rat`.

## Prices page

`page-template-prices.php` includes the same `calculator.php` without fixed key (full program picker).

## Maintenance

- Calculator/script changes: update `apps-script/`, redeploy web app URL in `js-css.php` if deployment ID changes.
- After taxonomy rewrite changes affecting `promocje`: flush permalinks.
